#Bin lun cc trng hp ca mdelta

    print("Nghiem kep: x = ", str(-b/2/a))

if delta<0:
    print("Phuong trinh vo nghiem")

    print("X1 = " + str((-b+delta**0.5)/2/a))
    print("X2 = " + str((-b-delta**0.5)/2/a))

#nh dng bng format cho php cn l phong ph
# cn gia: ' aaaa '
'{:^10}'.format('aaaa')
# cn l tri: 'aaaa '
'{:<10}'.format('aaaa')
# cn l phi ' aaaa'
'{:>10}'.format('aaaa')
# cn l phi, thay khong trng bng -: '------aaaa'
'{:->10}'.format('aaaa')
# cn l tri, thay khong trng *: 'aaa******'
'{:*<10}'.format('aaaa')
# cn gia, thay khong trng bng +: '+++aaaa+++'

print("s4:", s4)   # {1, 2, 3, ..., 99}

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn import linear_model, metrics

# c d liu t file csv
df = pd.read_csv("nguoi.csv", index_col = 0)
print(df)
# v biu  minh ha dataset
plt.plot(df.Cao, df.Nang, 'ro')
plt.xlabel('Chiu cao (cm)')
plt.ylabel('Cn nng (kg)')
plt.show()
In[]:
# s dng hi quy tuyn tnh
X = df.loc[:, ['Cao']].values
y = df.Nang.values

# X l d liu u vo
# y l d liu u ra
# loi m hnh
# tp hun trn d liu

model = linear_model.LinearRegression()
model.fit(X, y)
# in mt s thng tin v m hnh
mse = metrics.mean_squared_error(model.predict(X), y)
print("Tng bnh phng sai s trn tp mu:", mse)
print("H s hi quy:", model.coef_)
print("Sai s:", model.intercept_)
print(f"Cng thc: [Nng] = {model.coef_} x [Cao] +
{model.intercept_}")
In[]:

plt.scatter(X, y, c='b')
plt.plot(X, model.predict(X))
plt.show()
